      "review_summary": "The PR adds `crabbox run --require-artifact <glob>`, required-artifact collection and delegated-provider rejection plumbing, tests, run/artifact docs, and a Data Runs design-plan document.\n\nReproducibility: not applicable. This PR adds a new `crabbox run` flag and proposal docs rather than reporting a current-main bug. Source inspection confirms current main lacks the flag, and the PR supplies tests but no real-run proof.",
